wdi2-NY.GDS.TOTL.CN.def: Gross domestic savings are calculated as GDP less final consumption expenditure (total consumption). Data are in current local currency.
wdi2-NY.GDS.TOTL.CN.name: Gross domestic savings
wdi2-NY.GDS.TOTL.CN.source: World Bank national accounts data, and OECD National Accounts data files.
